description: The file initializes the React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It also imports necessary dependencies including React, ReactDOM, and the main CSS and App component files.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into the specified DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM, in this case wrapping App with React.StrictMode.
